dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Anthony Anderson. May I have your name, please?
Nice to meet you, Heather. Could you please provide me with your policy number and date of birth for verification purposes?
Of course. My policy number is five zero seven two three and my date of birth is one two zero six nineteen eighty-five.
Thank you, Heather. I also need your current address to update our records. Can you please spell out your street name and provide the city and zip code?
Certainly. My street name is M-A-I-N S-T-R-E-E-T, in Boston, zero two one one five.
Thank you for the information, Heather. Is there anything else I can assist you with today regarding your policy or coverage?
No, that's all for now. Thank you.
You're welcome, Heather. If you have any further questions, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
